[assistant] Fixed the failing negative-path test.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Root cause:
[assistant] - Changing `java.io.tmpdir` at test runtime was not reliable because the JDK temp-file helper may cache the temp directory before the test changes the property.
[assistant] - As a result, Mockito inline initialization succeeded, and the test hit the fallback `Expected inline mock maker initialization to fail`.
[assistant] 
[assistant] Updated approach:
[assistant] - The isolated child-first Mockito classloader now has an option to hide only:
